name: Framed Anthony Burill Poster
description:
When YH Associates faced difficulties, Sylvia moved on to become an independent consultant and later fulfilled her longtime dream of starting her own design consultancy, Design by Friends. 
This print, by Anthony Burill, was given to Sylvia by a former colleague to inspire her work-life balance in her new endeavor. This Burill design has been copied endless times and has now become ubiquitous.
